headline: Trump Says He and Putin Agreed to Begin Talks on Ending Ukraine War
summary: President Trump said he spoke with Russia’s Vladimir Putin and Ukraine’s Volodymyr Zelensky in an effort to bring the war to an end “as fast as possible.”  President Trump said he and Russia’s  Vladimir Putin  on Wednesday had agreed to open immediate talks to end the war in Ukraine in a “lengthy and highly productive phone call” between the two leaders.  “I believe this effort will lead to a successful conclusion, hopefully soon!” Trump wrote on Truth Social, the first official acknowledgment that the two leaders have talked since Trump was elected.

headline: WK Kellogg Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates, Volume Declines Y/Y
summary: KLG Q4 results show lower net sales but higher earnings. The gross margin expands 130 bps y/y on cost discipline and operational efficiency improvements.

headline: WK Kellogg Co (KLG) Q4 2024 Earnings Call Highlights: Strategic Progress Amid Sales Challenges
summary: Despite a decline in net sales, WK Kellogg Co (KLG) achieved EBITDA growth and improved gross margins, while setting the stage for future innovations and supply chain modernization.
